# 3 MongoDB 新增 Collection

### collection: `analysis_jobs`

```json
{
  "_id": ObjectId,
  "job_id": "uuid string",
  "user_id": "发起用户 ID",
  "team_id": "可选，家长查看孩子数据时需要",
  "target_user_id": "被分析的用户 ID（默认等于 user_id，家长场景下为孩子的 ID）",

  "prompt": "用户的自然语言问题",

  "status": "pending | generating | running | success | failed | cancelled",

  "generated_code": "Claude 生成的 Python 代码",

  "result": {
    "summary": "分析结论（文本）",
    "data": {},
    "chart_base64": "可选，图表的 base64 PNG"
  },

  "stdout": "",
  "stderr": "",
  "error": "",

  "created_at": "datetime (UTC)",
  "started_at": "datetime (UTC)",
  "finished_at": "datetime (UTC)",

  "timeout_sec": 30,
  "docker_container_id": "",

  "model": "claude-haiku-4-5-20251001",
  "token_usage": {
    "input_tokens": 0,
    "output_tokens": 0
  }
}
```

### 索引

```python
await db.db.analysis_jobs.create_index("job_id", unique=True)
await db.db.analysis_jobs.create_index([("user_id", 1), ("created_at", -1)])
await db.db.analysis_jobs.create_index("status")
```

索引代码添加到 `lumie_backend/app/core/database.py` 的 `create_indexes()` 函数中。

